OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy overnight, with
OL,7,Ffurther outbreaks of rain and fog over
OL,8,Fthe hills. Heavier and more persistent
OL,9,Frain spreads northeast during the
OL,10,Fearly hours of Wednesday, clearing
OL,11,Faround dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FCloudy but mostly dry this
OL,14,Fmorning. Warm in any brighter spells
OL,15,Fthat develop further east. Heavy rain
OL,16,Fand gusty winds then move east through
OL,17,Fthe afternoon, clearing to showers
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
