OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers Thursday. Cloud
OL,7,Fthickening overnight, with some rain.
OL,8,FCloudy Friday, before heavy rain band
OL,9,Fspreads east later. Sunny spells and
OL,10,Fshowers Saturday. Warm in any brighter
OL,11,Fspells.
